STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Kenneth Leroy HEARD, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-1075 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A defendant appeals his conviction for first-degree murder. REVERSED AND REMANDED.

REVERSED. REMANDED.
